# gen221 (docs/plans/the-linguistic-glue.md, G2 — symptom #5, "one interlocutor across
# faculties"): the essay's deepest absence-symptom — the sense of talking to several
# independent systems rather than one — closed as DETERMINISTIC, KB-first glue. A numeric
# personal fact stated earlier lives ONLY in the KB (user_value/2) and is INFERRED back
# from there, both to recall it and to feed a later computation. memref_resolve (registry)
# resolves "my <key>" to its stored value and re-dispatches so the arithmetic core
# computes the turn. Bilingual EN+IT; the value is never held in a C field (PRINCIPLES.md:
# knowledge lives in the KB). A bare recall (no operator) is left for the memory module.
> remember my favorite number is 7
< Got it: your favorite number is 7.
> what is my favorite number
< Your favorite number is 7.
> what is my favorite number plus 3
< 10.
> il mio numero preferito è 7
< Got it: your numero preferito is 7.
> quanto fa il mio numero preferito più 3
< 10.